data.description: This charming one story dream home sits nestled in Enclave at Bridgewater and boast three bedrooms (possibly 4) plus study, two full baths, open concept  living, dining and kitchen, two car garage and is ready for you to call   home! Remodeled in Nov/Dec of 2023 with recent paint, floors  and back fence ! This beauty is ready for you to move in and just enjoy! You will love the design and the flow of this home from the tucked away primary bedroom, spacious home office or possible 4th bedroom to the secondary bedrooms situated away from the family room. Enjoy owning your own home and not paying someone else’s mortgage! Located between and just minutes to Cypress and Katy, this is a great spot close to shopping and dining as well as hospitals ! Seeing is believing, you dont want someone else claiming your new address ! Welcome home to 3714 Granite Springs !
